title: Check Out
text: The Check Out is at "Victor Babeș" National Institute, between 09:00 and 13:00.

title: Who supports the IMSCB?
text:
Created over 20 years ago, from the pure desire of the romanian medical students to share their knowledge and skills all over the world, the International Medical Students’ Congress of Bucharest is extending its borders globally for the 3rd time, between the 4th and 8th of December 2019. 

Our efforts have been cosntantly supported by the amazing parteners: AQUA Carpatica, Domeniile Sâmburești, Alphasigma and many more that decided to stand next to us in order to provide you the best experience. Intertwining the passion of medicine with the will to offer students’ the opportunity to broaden their knowledge and train their medical skills, the IMSCB is the result of a long working proces.
